{"he760bb23g2fd0g4f54gbb39g1a4bf1fb3b2e": ["Only going to ask you one more time, boy. Hand over my locket. ", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "491a40a9-031d-7bb5-4d04-e8465e9b3c38"], "h941e1cf9gf8c3g4f7cg9c9cg802db4b7802b": ["I don't have your ugly locket. I've never even seen it before!", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "66a2a68f-aa45-fa06-0101-f28a3293b16e"], "hf1c78d8dgdfb8g48f4ga8f1gdd75b52cc817": ["Hand it over or I'll slap the teeth out of your head. ", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "db2c5542-9ae8-f104-cc19-d673c88ed37d"], "hfc4cfe07g09ddg49ffg94f9gf8ab063c85bf": ["Relax. The boy's good, but I'm better - here's your locket.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "ef213461-719e-c836-3e09-22fa6c9a61a5"], "hc16b89d3g5cfcg4b1eg8906g5ff2f4518f1b": ["Not bad. Not even a little bit bad.", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "7d63a52d-f615-c113-d0ab-d5fc3d9378f1"], "ha52b33aeg2ca6g467ag9a03gc442cc64d966": ["Can't thank you enough. ", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "530da8d8-4a5f-8524-7ace-428d2e040d8e"], "hdd7f7e9ag1d3dg4a35g81c1g348cb3438346": ["And you! Stay out of my pockets!", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "d2cf2c91-ca42-6b38-3a7a-703df2dd8372"], "h31a91f36gb6a2g4cddg8803g8b64ce99047f": ["Don't you dare lay a finger on that child.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "c7b3935f-9297-fd97-bd35-447aa44c8903"], "h8f8ffbbcgbde6g4f7ag9747g78e2866fbece": ["You threatening me?", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "a43da069-00a2-718c-7b44-f8355ac15bb8"], "h3a37c55ag32e5g4a23g9f6eg7035a6a8be42": ["Forget it. I don't want any trouble.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "b5449031-364f-66ba-e15a-083d582bd8fa"], "hb8e032b0ga101g475bg992dg7b5c501964f3": ["And I thought <i>he was a </i>coward. ", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "9a92fe5c-0a7e-f689-3831-03417745a86f"], "h60f135c3g4027g4d52gab8dgf2606c86d365": ["Do it, you gutless stinksack!", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "3b5a9d11-e125-b0f7-f455-ef5a5c436b70"], "hf2c316c8g2619g4480gaa1ag3824200d2e6c": ["Ahh!", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "98e5192c-577d-43f8-17d7-652d0c8f0706"], "h76a905aega527g4b95g8f19g82540923ca51": ["Knew it. Bloody well knew it. ", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "97e58861-70e4-367c-63ca-28edf64e6cdd"], "h62a324bfg55ccg4f9eg9916g92523565e704": ["You like watching people hit kids? You happy now?", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "86bce21d-9f03-bfed-ba03-f1efc9ef6bcb"], "h6ac7baabgab5ag4a73g979dg5f3872d0ef26": ["You're sick. ", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "07960d73-3cb5-ee8e-71f0-bad1db013e0a"], "hceca0abcg80a5g4fbeg9c5bgb52a5d816502": ["Feel better? Or were you hoping I'd cry?", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "6fc319b8-1693-5e30-5b78-b12f494eb0dd"], "h43458507gdbadg451cgb6a9g9968c482d992": ["You like watching people hit kids? You happy now?", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "4f13cec0-33ba-ba56-ba3e-4fe8212f9897"], "h18de6440g614eg4e15gaa76gf02de2b1354a": ["You're sick. ", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "122267b1-ca38-8932-11d1-2e5f21cbbe44"], "h8de38ef5g477cg4814g8d08g1402c1bfecd8": ["You're the one making threats - to a child. Pull yourself together.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "51a8ff11-0b2e-2e3f-84bb-e91386fbacf2"], "he2299a1ag97feg4870gbbdcgae1e2fa50b8f": ["You don't understand! The kid stole my locket! He... aw, the hells with this.", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "df6fbd6e-3569-9603-b2fb-83f78b6f3363"], "hb84a7418gb487g44d7gab3bg4e86b886c116": ["These little devils get away with everything because of coddling bastards like you. ", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "6f8fa2d1-9df2-7c21-915d-c67b052cd380"], "h591d2726gd1bcg4123gbd8dgfa86099814de": ["You'll get yours some day. I hope I get to see it.", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "f47ed0e8-77a7-4955-921f-734f5b9ee1aa"], "h7df04e9ag34efg43cfga472gb14fba61c793": ["Maybe you will. But personally, I doubt it.", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "0aaf3b7a-332e-8067-eade-8a50f29370d5"], "h73c6f708g5f77g4b38gadd8g43fc8f943d5f": ["See you around. ", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "fd2d54db-5609-2ce2-27a5-39c45dec5f90"], "ha0c39cb8gd419g458cg8f25g28e5491345c7": ["Him, I'll hit once. You won't be so lucky. Get out of the way. ", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "e3a15fb1-7dd2-4b6a-50e8-9e9ea036e169"], "h87530b79ga074g473cgb78fg0c6379b5af89": ["Whatever you do to the child, I'll repay ten-fold.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "506d37c5-813f-636e-a26e-5f07173186ad"], "h382df44cg9a7eg4604g9efdg6002c877fcd5": ["Raise a hand to that child and you'll lose it. Your choice.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "54252374-dffe-b104-e012-9c077f429426"], "hbc09e24dgdc25g4504g84c4g945b49cd39be": ["You don't scare me.", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "dbf1b96d-4390-0727-e88d-8a3b7e7d7699"], "h37ab238fg86fdg44a3ga930g67f1de2749e7": ["Gods, don't bleed over the thing. It's just tin and glass.", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "49beddc5-c6ff-bb22-bb83-b33dfc669128"], "h89f83905g4f50g4518g8342g9096bdad5ea9": ["Guards! This human is trying to hurt me and my friend!", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "b42e1524-2586-3b27-d80c-ac393b0b5c80"], "hd1b5fffbgc39fg4d8eg8bf5g0da66264b98c": ["Just warning. I've dealt with your type before, human.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "c7f00a75-45ef-0013-6a5a-f3cf8311793f"], "hbd1f4d6bg725fg4f16g9252g7da7b6a8e95f": ["You better do what he says, boy.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "b64ed85b-c649-d9f5-c72e-dea2152e74aa"], "h6f9be58bgf6bcg4209gb75bg356b58bf73cd": ["I said I don't have it. Maybe he dropped it running away from those big, scary goblins. ", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "a15e94fa-91af-f18b-c9f2-db725ae85ad3"], "h9a80937cgc69eg41e9gb531g2c2b9c94035c": ["You little split-tongued freak!", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "d866acd0-4fea-e1aa-2bba-3828ae96e445"], "ha3342968gbfc4g41a4gbc93g7e67142b5501": ["You're not fooling anyone, boy. Why'd you take it?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "0adb92cc-e247-fc98-dcd9-9ca8ef3a4ef3"], "h7cbe5fe6g249ag4d6dg8534ga406080d99ab": ["What kind of question is that? Why does anyone steal anything? ", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "676e4e6b-401a-4b02-73de-75af75f99041"], "h4921b91ag8d61g450agb44cga73c2c3b73a8": ["<i>Fine.</i> I have the stupid amulet. Take it.", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "bf061120-f625-b8df-07a3-a888e48449eb"], "h2bae8394g8fc0g4467g9996ga787538bd2d6": ["I want an answer - why'd you steal it?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "56d59fb3-4419-0be1-b762-00e0f56129f2"], "h4669d2fdg39edg4cd4g9ac4gdd02a753aa07": ["To impress a girl, most like. ", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "ab69fd84-94f7-c9e4-09d6-39c07dfe6958"], "hb35ac773g7909g44f2gbac4g0943cacede4c": ["It looked like my mother's, all right?", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "8106156b-a9a5-2c90-a8c4-17177023d950"], "h18ae2adfg9acag471aga1cfgd117b4feba3a": ["Just take the damn thing and leave me alone!", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "f3b05dba-4177-edf4-2502-59315ab3d38a"], "h5abd30e9geefag429eg9559g10b136fc9691": ["Keep it, kid. You need it more than me.", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "3f6d61c7-d9f9-c04e-7662-1e6f7a60f41f"], "h14a45afegb5eag4b82gaad5gbf6eff648c82": ["Poor kid. ", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "fd6cbfa9-bed5-7c40-af26-cb315ec63e39"], "h8eb6500fg1bd2g4140g9581g80edcf5e8be6": ["And I... huh. Someone stole it from me. That's kind of funny.", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "3ecdd5a5-66da-6cdc-aeea-3387ee8a4838"], "h59a4cc78ge5b7g4481gbe1dgab2b0dbf5f12": ["Yeah? I'll give you something to laugh about.", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "701ff5ac-b800-8881-eccd-87f59910ef22"], "h2eab8a67g33e7g4640g877dg60b47758e43c": ["Help! This human is trying to kill me!", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "7ef7cdd4-4ef1-da37-4018-fff9db688ec4"], "h3f252170ga8eeg4705ga551g79026a2e66e4": ["Good. Everyone happy?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "4943a0ed-5b2b-6672-4240-d8654f4ef38b"], "h5c37199bg9b1eg456dg9f78g8e43a91608df": ["There. Don't know why you cared so much. It's junk.", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "e79f2948-9df4-adb3-9c50-06df276dc342"], "h46999cfag7abbg452ag9f9cgf4288cd87a14": ["Scram before I give <i>you </i>something to care about.", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "c8d3bacb-5305-714f-73c6-092aef21530e"], "hd0e70392g0540g4bd5gb90bg8329a4d689b7": ["Kid's lucky you were here.", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "ba52a4cd-7fcb-5904-0ce8-cf1c73581375"], "hc8ec6853g8502g4177gb031g45469af2776d": ["Good, that's settled. Now, <i>disperse</i>. ", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "472eb4c5-93ff-f203-ff90-6ac560144a18"], "h21d35ad7g0fe2g4cabg9f4cg10d897028cb8": ["Huh. Someone stole it from me. That's kind of funny. ", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "8db6aad1-4e7a-9064-603c-4b252c702792"], "hc5057a6eg324eg458fg9a6age2335aa0ee3d": ["For the last time, I don't have the stupid thing!", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "c7db4393-49b1-6295-f03c-b2f17342fb9d"], "h270402bdgba1eg457dga24dg51665c6ecc33": ["Do you really want to take a beating over some jewellery?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "02bf855b-29d3-4948-b27b-554eb6ead501"], "hd319aff2gd6c5g4df7g8842g82726b0eaf64": ["Probably not. It's just tin and glass.", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "1afcb63c-e147-496e-c942-61245d37330d"], "h8fd72b62g5d4fg4b7fgb7b0g0f22fdd9af83": ["Here, take it. Not sure why you care so much about it, honestly.", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "f1a66b06-efa3-59cf-e6f3-8d77891ed8db"], "h5f9ccf92g4f86g41dfg8902g3524f4d34202": ["A beating, huh? Oh no. Whatever will I do?", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "3d66292d-9580-9a2d-bda5-1a847e5bb0db"], "hb387fd28gbb7cg4097gb71bgaac91c377077": ["Guards! Help me!", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "eb47794e-a3f4-dfb8-99f4-0f50ad671b91"], "h018a7122gb97dg49dfgb500g97f739893762": ["Doesn't look like they're coming, boy. ", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "97a1f202-1a5b-8d99-2632-851870b03ed3"], "hace11fa1gb2ceg4cd6g9322g8c5aefb3a03b": ["Fine, lumpy. You win.", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "57a2bb67-0f1c-dc1b-7c89-744222dd677d"], "h5bfa37d8g1941g4b37ga8a0g276ab71c89b0": ["I tried to give you a chance. You're on your own.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "21148fef-c550-5d2d-39f2-fcd66d0231c8"], "h612c29afg0b73g4c4dg8b49g337e0664bd38": ["Just give it back, boy. You're better than this.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "4766cedd-6dd3-7725-ba99-3782e4e358c6"], "h5dac429agcf7dg4baeg91d6gab0d6430b3fa": ["Fine! It's just tin and glass anyway.", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "2d9f4a08-f8aa-a7a8-7d77-d7b21356b42f"], "he442d30ag5b93g4f69g9386g306eac14f9eb": ["Better do what he says, boy. There's already one thief to bury today.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "0a8301e2-640f-9e59-beb3-2581e8e95ea3"], "haee63867g2485g4271g8518g1f9b99bda708": ["<i>Keep quiet and watch.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "ee9ce898-9a94-2bca-aeb3-6dfced1c6e15"], "h464b4d3ag13d3g46ceg85ecga6020d2f99f2": ["What's happening here?", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "fc7fb9b2-f937-e8e6-4b54-894a997bac48"], "h90526087g8555g4832g900eg6c56345be5bc": ["These two outsiders are threatening me, Ikaron.", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "017834d5-d34f-a1c2-a06f-c34f4269c98a"], "hbe538013ge141g452eg90f2ge77c0b4f7a99": ["Is this true?", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "246424a7-43f2-e2f5-ba54-1080de009899"], "h2ab727cfga7d4g4943ga64ag8f599596738f": ["The boy stole my locket!", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "6c9c58f3-1319-4b4f-69ec-69e713c77d7d"], "h7498b704g8d3cg4cb0g9e78g87497a4d7f62": ["And that justifies threatening a child?", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "a731d866-824e-4609-de04-b61fc178db1e"], "hda5750a2g9a91g4293g816fga123b323a6b6": ["There's no locket. This bastard's just throwing his weight around.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "b193222d-22f8-1698-c74a-3c3e00c44b38"], "hfe19b564g15e0g4156g8ff2g82036762b947": ["You godsdamned snake!", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "e4d0394b-3572-60ad-c35b-b8df609366f3"], "h215397cdg0ff1g4d94g9293g1156386a5335": ["Go, child.", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "377e552d-b540-c178-e24c-7ff7507b7434"], "hf2f2aeefg7564g4686ga835g1635786f466e": ["And you? You had this coming. ", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "a203c260-bb89-0f81-19dc-2b2112a68a1e"], "h7679b166g6324g417fgad93g21dee98d7609": ["And stay down.", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "0712a0f9-9d6a-4419-f9ac-1923bbdb44d9"], "h2a14cd10gf656g48bdgabd3gc38d5721bcc3": ["Nobody's hurting the boy - he's free to leave when he wants.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "bd553e68-48bc-e27b-c1a0-ac36f54907f2"], "h9ce74d0dgbcb2g4fd6gbaebg79fc77036a2e": ["Good. You heard them, child. You're free to go.", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "7f29f4f1-fb52-857d-d913-46438742036f"], "ha5f57bb0gdf91g4a14g961bge5a4bad6194c": ["But my locket!", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "6070fe86-745c-ab92-7394-1a5cf262bf24"], "h03d38605gebd5g4236g966ag183f35e79e17": ["<i>Quiet</i>. Child, go.", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "553b5b37-d3ce-52de-d2e6-c962dedd1283"], "h45f512f0gc74ag483dgb980gc2c5d256ba59": ["We were wrong to trust you. I see that now. ", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "27e78388-a9b1-3621-d7f4-3227ab9a79c8"], "hd0f26851g926fg4497g8558g4326866b2a33": ["Just a misunderstanding. The boy was about to give Barth his locket back.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "5c1be2ee-c40f-f781-c98a-7474bd5919f2"], "h9b55c8d7g0eacg463dgaec1g3ac3753e1825": ["You're lying. I see it in your face. ", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "f24ad966-3e38-e7dd-1585-24f9c20c2dab"], "h59eb906eg2b20g4ce8g99f4g046e22d3c884": ["Child, you promised to stop stealing. You disgrace us all. Give it back.", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "f5f74ac6-082c-d8f9-df48-2e66c3903592"], "heab650e9g5f06g4c81gbe6dgebdb33626896": ["Fine. It's worthless anyway. ", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "6cdefc83-6fdb-ff9e-903f-b487acd8e6ad"], "h674e591cg0e69g41d8ga623g2f0f387ceb25": ["Meddlers are even worse than thieves. You're not meddling, are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "1bc31296-cc42-c290-4065-633a596ea488"], "h989371a2g91bfg4965gba98g7139276296d0": ["Of... of course not. ", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "5966f14c-5db0-db5a-4e8e-a18cd8a829ec"], "h89477a48g72c5g439ega9d4gcab05c3d569b": ["And now you're threatening <i>me</i>? You fool.", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "3e9f587b-0677-142a-0478-94f0b6420501"], "hf74dfdc0g387bg4ac9g811bgbe740fd5e961": ["Sisters! Brothers! To arms!", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "2be39393-d787-6407-4e92-88179eff7239"], "ha7750388g7985g45e1g8751gf036781f1a82": ["I'm the one looking out for the boy.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "5e6efb76-b794-b914-eee6-5d72c2a8c8db"], "h7c7e60e7gfaeeg45f6g8065g77d5dc0ed83a": ["These two outsiders are threatening me, Ikaron. Even tails over there!", "94e865e9-790d-4633-a378-8fb50832b5e9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "d1ab391e-781d-c8c3-fed0-320a72228546"], "hc47a04d7g6b7cg4d91gae51gd9c075c5a918": ["What's happening here?", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "750e6bfc-9892-a09f-876d-e06fb7cbb7dc"], "h41e8c564g9db5g439bg9f93ga3b457fb53a1": ["The boy's a thief.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "578fb0ba-e579-d375-a25e-70d303596727"], "hcbaa7a15gcfc5g4742gae6ag14ece55243e4": ["And both of you thought striking the child was a suitable punishment? ", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "80040b49-4f75-65ab-85ea-171f1ce3be1e"], "hfde17347gc019g4539gabc4g5eaea2d1a75e": ["If his parents won't do it, I will. ", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "daf7ced8-7f11-915f-6901-2bab76dcaf21"], "h88892473ge96bg4a89gbbd5g8bcb5a0a71a6": ["He's an orphan. How'd you like it if I struck <i>you</i>?", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "0a47c81a-725e-67ea-9c4e-0894a6da4575"], "hb3f2754fgfbf1g4c40gac1ag0469cad50340": ["You raise a hand to me, it'd better have steel in it. ", "534bceaf-678c-40a0-8ca9-e1134f95ba0d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "d0a744ec-6fc3-2b94-cfd3-94bc5b6a1de1"], "h75f830adg5d43g4284g8800gba92e547ff0e": ["Let the boy take it as a warning - he's getting off lightly.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "a56091f6-adbf-096b-f777-06b299593a90"], "h012be5f6g4afdg4f72ga3a1g7d55983c3741": ["You're not wrong. I wish you were. ", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "3b09a69e-2c09-f833-5ecf-0ec5777e8245"], "h2aca2b58g66fag4291g85aagcb5184d1c279": ["Child, learn your lesson and be grateful. ", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "5068e6b3-5944-6d11-d46b-767a67d30ad0"], "h1aff7c5eg0060g491bg8a8cgf1916ee382a9": ["And you, get out of my sight. ", "03b6fae4-d250-4ce9-9a01-19cb427deb17", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "3641bf0b-2132-3324-9bc1-0a9ce0edf606"], "hb9dc47d6g0f8cg461eg8784g01fb5d9e6eb3": ["He's a thief. Is it any wonder people think that of us all?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "bafd2259-78bd-ab0a-9572-72d8d97e1088"], "h879df67eg8115g4bdag9ddega5095b222396": ["My coin's on the tiefling. He looks <i>angry</i>.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "825b8bd8-944e-2b0b-a96d-2fc117a0b31a"], "ha1567ddcg86cfg42fbgbf8cg0a800ca8b065": ["No idea. This man just started attacking the boy.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_RobbedAdventurer.html", "78481b51-fa9f-c9b9-c111-f58ae84a48cf"]}